<p style="color: #ff9c9d;">“This is the space for a quote (or multiple quotes) from an Oracle representative about their thoughts on a partnership with OneQode, what it means for  customers and the future. OCI is built to deliver better performance for enterprise customers, and we’re pleased to be working with OneQode to  deliver high-performance solutions to our customers in the game industry and enterprise space”, says Jane Doe, XYZ at Oracle.</p>
<p>“We’re incredibly excited. Oracle are leaders in their field, with a global footprint, extensive application suite and significant infrastructure pedigree. Further, they’ve got a proven track record as an excellent partner,” said Matt Shearing, OneQode CEO. “Similarly, OneQode are obsessive about delivering high-performance solutions for customers in industries like gaming. This partnership is therefore a real <em>‘one plus one equals three’</em> where together, we’ll be delivering unrivalled solutions for our customers.”</p>
<p>Oracle and OneQode will work to bring combined solutions to their customers, integrate their services and introduce Direct Connect functionality between OCI and OneQode Cloud. Going forward, Oracle and OneQode will also continue to explore new opportunities to bring high-performance solutions to users in spaces like gaming and beyond.</p>
